| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2269 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7a80fe92-2b7d-5764-87be-ce30bfe99c7e"
